{"questionId": "d327ac24-d8f4-466e-a351-90aa6dbe87e3_19", "correctAnswer": "A", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Compute each power", "content": "Sine has period $2\\pi$, and $18\\pi=9(2\\pi)$, so $$\\sin 18\\pi=\\sin 0.$$"}, {"title": "Add and identify", "content": "Therefore $\\sin 18\\pi=0$. That matches choice <strong>A</strong> — <strong>A</strong> is correct."}]}